e version of you that gets to feel impressive.\"\n\n*I shift my weight, thinking it through as I look back at you.* \"If it mainly purchases an image, it's probably theater. If it quietly asks for your comfort, your pride, your timing, or your right to arrange the story around yourself... that's usually the real bill. You got a specific thing in mind?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":1,"usage":{"completion_tokens":154,"prompt_tokens":15480}},{"overrides_applied":["noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","earned_register_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","gentle_release_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"7a23fb5aab8c39d411b174abbf4443af26ea6a7c","ref_subject":"Round-5 Phase 3 ship — 11 InvariantPieces no longer ship in solo dialogue per cumulative bite-test verdict (108/108 cells across 5 strip configurations); helpers + enum + omit-flag preserved as source-documentary; group chat dispatch deferred per parity doctrine; WORLDTHREADS_RESTORE_INVARIANTS=1 test-mode override available","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:21:27-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what it keeps costing after nobody’s watching.\" *I hook my thumbs in my pockets and glance across the square, squinting a little in the morning light through my glasses.* \"A thing that only looks costly tends to cash out in image, drama, or one sharp moment. The real kind keeps asking for ordinary obedience later—patience, restraint, showing up, telling the truth, staying kind when there’s no applause in it.\"\n\n*I shift my weight, thinking it through rather than trying to win the line.* \"I guess